cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image restoration using Markov random fields (MRFs) and proposes a new approach for learning the parameters in MRFs. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses techniques from bi-level optimization, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the efficiency of inference, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM).
